Class AddressEntity

java.lang.Object
  at.fhv.roomanizer.persistence.entity.person.AddressEntity

public class AddressEntity
extends java.lang.Object

Every Person has exactly one Address, which represents the "main living place" and foremost, the billing address. To simplify matters, address also contains informations like email, phone and fax. The hotel contacts every type of person through this piece of data.
